{"obj_edit_time":"1769149728","blocks":[{"block_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf","block_type":1,"children":["doxjp5q82OgFmb5NlYZILBdM0jh","doxjpIh2tBy66eiuHJbbGzozIif","doxjpjdvqx1VIu854pJRMilUMod","doxjp8CsEisHNuslDT2jEAqiWne","doxjpv9Zin4YtTBO6omIuY8xb0y","doxjp5pwSmQIBJ14fMrXnEgAQfg","doxjps9F2W8Nafq7bpf1vLtJW0e","doxjp46MyydDI54am8F9ho7jxHe","doxjpy6dnjRIFttG9LxbNbGF3Mg"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxjp5q82OgFmb5NlYZILBdM0jh","block_type":14,"code":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"slug: EB3dwd6IsiGHgZkjzYJcfh6Onw0\ntitle: 業務介紹\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"sidebar_position: 0","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"language":67,"wrap":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"},{"block_id":"doxjpIh2tBy66eiuHJbbGzozIif","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"},{"block_id":"doxjpjdvqx1VIu854pJRMilUMod","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"},{"block_id":"doxjp8CsEisHNuslDT2jEAqiWne","block_type":2,"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券業務中的資產賬戶是指客戶在證券公司或券商開立的一個專門用於持有和交易證券的帳戶。這個賬戶通常用於存放客戶的投資資金和證券，並且用於執行相關的買賣、交易和結算活動。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpv9Zin4YtTBO6omIuY8xb0y","block_type":2,"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"同時，證券業務下的後台資產流水主要用於追踪和記錄資產在證券公司內部的流動和流向。它是證券公司後台系統中的一個重要模塊，主要用於管理和監控客戶資產的流轉過程，保障交易的準確性、安全性和合規性。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjp5pwSmQIBJ14fMrXnEgAQfg","block_type":2,"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"除了業務流水查詢，另外，在日常業務中，後台業務人員主要會使用以下操作功能：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjps9F2W8Nafq7bpf1vLtJW0e","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"調賬 ：調賬是指對賬戶內的資金、證券或其他資產進行核對和調整的過程。後台業務人員可以使用調賬功能來比對賬戶內的交易數據、結算數據和其他相關信息，以確保賬戶的準確性和一致性。調賬操作通常包括比對交易記錄、結算記錄、資金流水和證券持倉等，並解決其中的差異或錯誤。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"},{"block_id":"doxjp46MyydDI54am8F9ho7jxHe","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"資產凍結：資產凍結是指對特定資產或賬戶進行限制或禁止處置的操作。後台業務人員可以使用資產凍結功能針對特定情況或要求，對資產或賬戶進行凍結，以防止非授權的操作或保護利益。資產凍結可以是臨時的，例如在調查期間或法律程序中，也可以是長期的，例如根據法律要求或客戶要求。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"},{"block_id":"doxjpy6dnjRIFttG9LxbNbGF3Mg","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"臨時調賬：通常是指暫時性的賬戶調整，用於處理特殊情況或錯誤的處理。這些調整通常是暫時性的，並在後續進行進一步核對和調整。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"T1qTdusEWoMT9bx7XJqjRYE6prf"}]}